06:34.466 --> 06:39.631
I will make with you an everlasting covenant my steadfast sure love for David.

06:41.092 --> 06:48.720
And then we turned Isaiah 53 and we saw the purchase of the suffering servant.

06:48.740 --> 06:51.463
Isaiah is saying that 700 years before Jesus.

06:52.704 --> 06:53.745
That's stunning prophecy.

06:53.865 --> 06:54.866
But then he comes.

06:55.426 --> 06:56.287
and fulfills it.

06:57.108 --> 07:02.153
