14:08.839 --> 14:13.106
So he says in Matthew 516, let your light so shine

14:13.378 --> 14:18.927
among others that they may see your good deeds and give glory to your Father who is in heaven."

14:19.568 --> 14:20.289
That's how he lived.

14:20.569 --> 14:21.851
That's how he teaches us to live.

14:22.412 --> 14:28.702
And he says in John 15, 8, by this is my Father glorified that you bear much fruit.

14:31.807 --> 14:35.934
