14:37.536 --> 14:38.658
This is really significant.

14:39.800 --> 14:41.042
I mean, this is an amazing moment.

14:41.602 --> 14:43.805
They ask Him and they've been around Him.

14:43.845 --> 14:44.826
They've seen His life.

14:44.886 --> 14:46.108
